    <title type="html"><![CDATA[使用substance美化Java Swing界面]]></title>
    <link href="http://comflag.github.com/blog/2012/05/18/shi-yong-substancemei-hua-java-swingjie-mian/"/>
    <updated>2012-05-18T20:07:00+08:00</updated>
